Hoi Kiw
Summersalt - Kamai Ia Ka Hok
KAMAI IA KA HOK
Jingduh jingkyrmen, ka pynlong ia ngi 
Ban shaniah h’u Blei, ka hok ieng sakhi
Wat ai jingisih kan teh mraw shyrta
Ban bud ki kyntien sneng i mei i pa

Lano ka pyrthei kan iohi ia ngi?
Symboh jingpyrkhat, kin mait ia lynti
Thang iaka sharak, ha ri ka ba dum
Wat ai ba kan lip, wat buh hapoh khrum

Kamai iaka hok, u ba rim na mynwei - U pynbna ia kane
Phet iap na ka thok, ki rongphong ka pyrthei.
Da pynkup ialade
Iktiar ka mynta, ki thied mynbarim
Ka wait ka jingstad, kine dei ban shim
Ngin bah la lyngkor, ngin thom sha ki kliar
Haba kut ka sngi, ngin ioh khulom ksiar
Kamai iaka hok

Haba ka jingsniew, ka thombor naphang
To tip ba jingbha – iaki kan kyndang
Ka bamsap kan tlor, baroh ngin iohi
Iaka roi ka par, ngi kren kein ia phi

Ngin lah beit ban leh, haba mon ka jwat
Ka por ban kynthih, ngim dei ban pyrkhat
Iawer ia baroh, ngin klet jingiapher
Kamai iaka hok, long iing to ngin ker

U Tirot Sing - famous king of Khasi hill kingdom
